channel.title: Need Coders
channel.description:
Hi. This is my first time making a server, so I really am lost. But, luckily, I managed to get the server up and running. Up and running, but without any cool effects, commands, etc. I have NO idea how to code this, and was wondering if a few good coders could help. I'm up for pretty much anything they want in the game.
And the coders will have to tell me what to do for them so they're able to code.
